CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 21, 1960, pg. 20, reads: "Action - Fast-stepping 135-pound Bobby Reeves of the Daniels A. C. (back to camera) and William Sheppard, East Liberty Gym, slug it out in the matches held at the Centre Avenue YMCA last week. Reeves won the decision. It was one of the best bouts of the evening. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boxers Bobby Reeves and William Sheppard in boxing match in Centre Avenue YMCA
